  "body": "This issue is specific to the web application eips.ethereum.org.\r\n\r\nSome pages (e.g. https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-721) display poorly on mobile. See:\r\nhttps://twitter.com/yugacohler/status/1393606548337958918\r\n\r\nThis appears to be caused the the table of metadata at the top of pages. I bet this could be fixed with a relatively simple CSS update to force the table to wrap vs. overflow. The goal should be to constrain all mobile content to 100% page width in order to avoid any content overflow.",
